### Arabic

فَأَخَذْنَـٰهُ وَجُنُودَهُۥ فَنَبَذْنَـٰهُمْ فِى ٱلْيَمِّ وَهُوَ مُلِيمٌ

### English

So We seized him and his soldiers, casting them into the sea while he was blameworthy.